'''乔安娜·柯尔'''（{{lang-en|Joanna Cole}}，{{bd|1944年|8月11日|2020年|7月12日|catIdx=Cole}}），美国[[儿童文学|儿童文学]]及[[科普|科普]]作家，一生创作了超过250本科普书，其中《神奇校车》系列故事享誉世界<ref name="Hollwood">{{cite news|url=https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/joanna-cole-dead-author-magic-school-bus-book-series-dies-at-75-1303345|title=Joanna Cole, Author of 'The Magic School Bus' Book Series, Dies at 75|last=Perez|first=Lexy|publisher=Hollywood Reporter|date=2020-07-16|accessdate=2020-07-16|archive-date=2020-07-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200716113525/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/joanna-cole-dead-author-magic-school-bus-book-series-dies-at-75-1303345|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

==生平==
1944年生于新澤西州[[紐華克_(新澤西州)|紐華克]]。她的父亲马里奥是房屋油漆工；母亲伊丽莎白是[[家庭主妇|家庭主妇]]<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2020/07/16/books/joanna-cole-dead.html|title=Joanna Cole, Who Imagined Fantastical Bus Rides, Dies at 75|date=2020-07-16|accessdate=2020-07-16|work=[[The_New_York_Times|The New York Times]]|archive-date=2022-05-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220503181012/https://www.nytimes.com/2020/07/16/books/joanna-cole-dead.html}}</ref>。她在东奥兰治的郊区长大<ref name="Hollwood"/><ref name="Silvey1995">{{cite book|author=Anita Silvey|title=Children's Books and Their Creators|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=graiX5o4tMYC&pg=PA154|year=1995|publisher=Houghton Mifflin Harcourt|isbn=0-395-65380-0|page=154|access-date=2020-07-21|archive-date=2020-07-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200727005512/https://books.google.com/books?id=graiX5o4tMYC&pg=PA154}}</ref>。她从小就热爱[[科学|科学]]，并认为阅读科学书是一件很平常的事<ref name="Ottawa">{{cite news|title=Magic School Bus makes a stop in Ottawa|url=https://www.newspapers.com/clip/55446700/the-ottawa-citizen/|newspaper=The Ottawa Citizen|date=1999-09-10|page=37|via=Newspapers.com|accessdate=2020-07-16|archive-date=2020-07-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200716030817/https://www.newspapers.com/clip/55446700/the-ottawa-citizen/}} {{free access}}</ref>。小时候，她经常在自家后院观察[[昆虫|昆虫]]和植物。她也喜欢上学，热衷于写科学报告<ref name="Silvey1995"/>。

[[1960年代|1960年代]]，她曾在[[马萨诸塞大学阿默斯特分校|马萨诸塞大学]]和[[印第安纳大学|印第安纳大学]]学习，最终在[[纽约市立学院|纽约市立学院]]获[[心理学|心理学]]学士学位<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://biography.jrank.org/pages/2117/Cole-Joanna-1944.html |title=Joanna Cole (1944–) Biography |accessdate=2010-04-04 |publisher=JRank.org |archive-date=2012-09-17 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6AkP5CloU?url=http://biography.jrank.org/pages/2117/Cole-Joanna-1944.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。经过专业培训后，她成为布鲁克林小学的一名[[圖書館員|图书管理员]]<ref name="Movie">{{cite web |url=https://movieweb.com/joanna-cole-dead-magic-school-bus/ |title=Joanna Cole Dies, The Magic School Bus Creator Was 75 |last=Orange |first=B. Alan |date=2020-07-15 |website=Movieweb |access-date=2020-07-16 |archive-date=2022-05-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220505025918/https://movieweb.com/joanna-cole-dead-magic-school-bus/ }}</ref>。随后，她担任《[[新闻周刊|新闻周刊]]》通讯员、[[學樂集團|學樂集團]]跷跷板读书俱乐部助理编辑、[[道布尔戴出版社|道布尔戴出版社]]儿童读物资深编辑等职<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.npr.org/2020/07/15/891586790/the-magic-school-bus-series-author-joanna-cole-has-died |title='The Magic School Bus' Series Author Joanna Cole Has Died |last=Tsioulcas |first=Anastasia |date=2020-07-15 |website=NPR |access-date=2020-07-16 |archive-date=2022-04-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220423021744/https://www.npr.org/2020/07/15/891586790/the-magic-school-bus-series-author-joanna-cole-has-died }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=https://archivessearch.lib.uconn.edu/repositories/2/resources/852 |title=Joanna Cole Papers |website=Archives & Special Collections, UConn Library |access-date=2020-07-16 |archive-date=2021-06-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210624041122/https://archivessearch.lib.uconn.edu/repositories/2/resources/852 }}</ref>。1971年，她出版了自己的第一本儿童读物《[[蟑螂|蟑螂]]》<ref name="Ottawa"/>。她的创作理由也很简单，因为当时没有关于这种昆虫的童书<ref name="Young2004">{{cite book|author=Greg Young|title=A Guide for Using The Magic School Bus Inside a Hurricane in the Classroom|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=L7OXgCkGcd0C&pg=PA4|date=2004|publisher=Teacher Created Resources|isbn=978-1-57690-089-5|pages=4|access-date=2020-07-21|archive-date=2020-07-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200723094130/https://books.google.com/books?id=L7OXgCkGcd0C&pg=PA4}}</ref>。1980年，她成为[[自由职业者|自由职业者]]，开始专业从事儿童文学创作，同时为《父母》杂志撰写儿童读物和文章<ref name="Movie"/>。[[1980年代|1980年代]]，她主要出版了两本亲子读物，《你是怎样来到这个世界的》（1984年）以及《你的新便盆》（1989年）。她说，能够做自己从小就喜欢的事是一种莫大的荣幸<ref name="Silvey1995"/>。

1985年，她开始创作《神奇校车》系列，并于1986年出版第一本《水的故事》。《神奇校车》系列取得了巨大的成功，并被翻译成多种语言，销售量达数百万本。其中卷毛老师的形象深入人心，陪伴孩子们去探索奇妙未知的世界<ref>{{cite web |author1=颜小鹂 |title=蒲公英童书馆总编辑颜小鹂悼念《神奇校车》作者乔安娜·柯尔 |url=https://www.thepaper.cn/newsDetail_forward_8331088 |publisher=[[澎湃新闻|澎湃新闻]] |date=2020-07-19 |accessdate=2020-07-21 |archive-date=2020-07-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200721023106/https://www.thepaper.cn/newsDetail_forward_8331088 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。《神奇校车》系列还被改编为由[[莉莉·湯姆琳|莉莉·湯姆琳]]主演的电视动画节目，自1994年起连续播出了18年之久。2017年，被改编为由[[凱特·麥金儂|凱特·麥金儂]]主演的[[Netflix|Netflix]]系列网络儿童剧场<ref name="Hollwood"/>。该系列的最新一部是《神奇校车：探索人类进化》，在2020年出版<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.pbs.org/newshour/arts/the-magic-school-bus-is-back-and-its-tackling-evolution |title=The Magic School Bus is back — and it's tackling evolution |last=Flock |first=Elizabeth |date=2019-09-06 |website=PBS |access-date=2020-07-16 |archive-date=2022-05-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220509224423/https://www.pbs.org/newshour/arts/the-magic-school-bus-is-back-and-its-tackling-evolution }}</ref>。

2020年7月12日因[[特发性肺纤维化|特发性肺纤维化]]在美国[[艾奥瓦州|艾奥瓦州]][[苏城_(艾奥瓦州)|苏城]]逝世<ref name="Hollwood"/><ref name = WSVN>{{cite web |title=‘Magic School Bus’ author Joanna Cole dies at age 75 |url=https://wsvn.com/news/us-world/magic-school-bus-author-joanna-cole-dies-at-age-75/ |publisher=WSVN 7News |accessdate=2020-07-16 |archive-date=2020-07-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200716134548/https://wsvn.com/news/us-world/magic-school-bus-author-joanna-cole-dies-at-age-75/ }}</ref>。

